headline: Telefonica's Q2 Earnings Match, Top Line Misses Estimates & Slides Y/Y
summary: TEF's Q2 net income plunges 67% but organic revenue rises 1.5% as it reshapes its portfolio and reaffirms 2025 guidance.

headline: ITRI Q2 Earnings Beat, Sales Lag, Stock Sinks 10% on Mixed Outlook
summary: Itron posts record Q2 2025 earnings and raises EPS outlook, but shares fall 10% on trimmed revenue forecast and mixed segment trends.
